title: The Challenge  dvd rip
description:
It&#039;s an action adventure/adventure comedy. They play estranged twins with very opposite personalities. Lizzie (Ashley) is very focused and driven, while Shane (Mary-Kate) is more relaxed, but concerned about the environment. Both girls are chosen for a Survivor-like popular game show with college scholarships as the prize

Shane is very into nature and Lizzie is not. They are complete opposites, or so they think. Both enter to be in a TV show and the producers of the show think it would be fun to put them both on the same team when they hate each other. Shane lives in Los Angeles with her mom and Lizzie in Washington, D.C. with her dad. They haven&#039;t seen each other in 2 years. They are both put on team Mayan and they have to try and get along for the sake of the team, and their college scholarships. They of course break some romance rules with some guys.
